The performance of the ANR Sector in the past decades has been constrained, mainly by:-
* Adverse climatic conditions from 1968 to present ( the draught of the Sahel -1980s);
* The Structural Adjustment Programs of the 1980s without sequencing;
* The Low Private Investment in value added agro industrial enterprises,
* The Declining international agricultural commodity prices and unfair trade;
* The Soaring Food Prices and high cost of agricultural inputs such as fertilizers etc;
* Weak agricultural research and poor extension delivery services;
